      "rationale": "Relative error between CFD-predicted NIH and experimental NIH computed at all 5 operating points. Maximum relative error was 13.4% at the highest flow-speed combination. Mean absolute relative error across all points was 7.8%. Validation metric satisfies the ±15% acceptance band established in the validation plan."
    },
