      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal use error assessment is not required. The CFD analysis was performed by an engineer with 8 years of experience in cardiovascular CFD and reviewed by a senior engineer. Analyst qualification is documented. No further assessment scoped for this COU."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
